text: Ic Osuuold arcebisceop þurh Godes giefe mid geþafunge & leafe Eadwardes Angulcyninges & Ælfheres Mercna heretogan & þæs heorodes on Weogornaceastre landes sumne dæl þæt syndIIhida butonLXæcran þæt hæft se arcebisceop genumen into Cymesige to his hame him to hwætelande þe fram cuþum mannum Wulfringctun is gehaten sumum cnihte þæm is noma Æþelwold mid allum þingum þe þarto belimpað freolice his dæge forgeaf & æfter his dæge twam yrfweardum & æfter heora forðsiþe to þære halgan stowe into Wiogornaceastre þæm bisceope to bryce.
Sie hit ælces þinges freoh buto ferdfare & walgeworc & brygcgeweorc & cyrcanlade.
Þis wæs gedon ymbeVIIIIhund wintra &VII& hundseofantig þæs þæ Drihtnes gebyrdtide wæsSancta Maria & sanctus Michahel cum sancto Petro& allum Godes halgum gemiltsien þis haldendum.
Gief hwa buton gewrihtum hit abrecan wylle God hine to rihtere bote gecyrre, amen.
